<section class="Sh">
<h1 class="Sh" id="CAVEATS"><a class="permalink" href="#CAVEATS">CAVEATS</a></h1>
<code class="Nm">screenblank</code> checks the access and modification times of
  the devices it is monitoring to determine activity. If the devices are on a
  file system mounted with the <code class="Cm">noatime</code> and/or
  <code class="Cm">nodevmtime</code> options, it will not function as expected.
  A possible workaround is to use a script as such:
<div class="Bd Pp Bd-indent">
<pre>
#!/bin/sh
/usr/sbin/screenblank -d 0 -e 0 &amp;&amp; read
/usr/bin/pkill screenblank
</pre>
</div>
